{
  "stem": "3040.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After the war, they were like two different people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The one in Brooklyn stayed Hasidic, and the other one became completely secular.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He also has-- he has two children, two daughters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he now has six grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they all live in Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they're very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in fact, I was in Israel only three weeks ago, when I saw the family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we had-- I have two sisters-- I had three sisters, one of whom survived the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her name is Rachel, 'Rah-kell,' and she lives in Queens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she's a widow now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She has only one daughter and two grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other two sisters, Cerel and Rebecca perished in the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, they were together with my parents when they were transported from the ghetto to some kind of a-- we assumed that it was Belzec that they were taken to.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Is Jakov,",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well as I said, until the age of about 14, I was walking in the footsteps of my family, of my father.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not that I stopped admiring them later on, but my interest became more diversified.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was reading a lot of books, Polish books, which was not necessarily approved by this-- by this community that I was raised in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I read all the-- most of the Polish classics.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very interested in poetry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was-- since I did not go to secular school, I was preparing myself to get the equivalent of a high school diploma, which was called matura in Polish, by taking private lessons.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I had very good tutors and eventually I've accomplished that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the primary school was the cheder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was from the age of three years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I grew up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I joined the yeshiva, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
